IWYUWrapper
-----------

Internal CMake script wrapper for IWYU (Include What You Use) command execution.

This module provides a placeholder wrapper for future enhancements to IWYU
command building and execution. Currently, the IWYU.cmake module handles
all command building directly.

This file is included for consistency with the ClangTidyWrapper pattern.

